# Project Zenith — environment variables (all OPTIONAL for the MVP).
# Every core data source is keyless: CelesTrak, OpenNotify, Nominatim (UA only),
# and astronomy-engine / tz-lookup run with no network. Copy to .env.local to set.

# MapTiler Cloud API key (server-side only; consumed by /api/maptiler/*).
# Required for Phase 2's 3D globe (raster texture, vector buildings, terrain, geocoding).
# Get one free at https://cloud.maptiler.com — free tier: 100k tile loads/mo.
# If unset, the globe falls back to OSM raster tiles (no buildings/terrain).
NEXT_PUBLIC_MAPTILER_KEY=

# Optional precision upgrade if the deferred Horizons route is enabled later.
# (Horizons itself needs no key; this is a placeholder for any future provider.)
# CESIUM_ION_TOKEN=
# N2YO_KEY=
